title: A Bar Song (Tipsy)

description.plain: “A Bar Song (Tipsy)” is a country song by Shaboozey released on April 12th 2024. The song is notable for featuring an interpolation of J-Kwon’s 2004 party anthem “Tipsy”. The song is a part of his 2024 album “Where I’ve Been, Isn’t Where I’m Going”
